---
title: Fillet-O-Barramundi Sandwiches with DIY Tartar Sauce and Roasted Potatoes
description: Craving fast food? This epic, breaded fish sandwich tastes like a takeout fake-out, complete with crunchy pickles and DIY tartar sauce! The tartar sauce also acts as delicious dipper for a side of golden potatoes.
